Yet another really boring photo style image of a another cute woman in her 20s with long, blonde hair and blue eyes, and dry, tanned skin who looks very generic. She is wearing an orange & blue knitted scenic jumper with the word "Testing" knitted in yellow on it. She is smiling and wears really dark-red lip-stick and black, gothic eye-shadow. Upper body only. She stands beside part of a painting of a trendy, bearded hipster barista dude who is inside a gaudy, 1950's style, North American New York diner. He is looking down towards his mobile phone (which has a cool rodent logo on it). Overall, everything is really detailed, with lots of intricate stuff going on. Inside the classic British Pub are the usual black and white wooden beams, hops, all that sort of thing. The black wallpaper with red roses on looks cool too. Colourful background, unreal 5, octane engine, trending on myspace, 35mm masterpiece quality, sharp focus, soft lighting cinematic movie film still, supereme quality. Rated 10/10 and given 5 stars on everything. universally aclaimed, even by aliens. Shockingly good image which actually looks real. Sort of. Just squint a bit.
